Subject: [PATCH] configs: Add CONFIG_MAX31856=m

Enable support for MAX31856 temperature sensors.

See: https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/issues/3915

Signed-off-by: Phil Elwell <phil@raspberrypi.com>
